Rating: 4
This was amazing. My husband said it was one of the best dishes he's ever had. I was tempted to skip the aioli, and was very glad I didn't. It was so easy and so tasty. We dipped the fish and the grilled veggies in it. We used the leftover couscous in the suggested Moroccan Chicken Salad with dates and mint. It was really good, too. We also used the leftover aioli and tuna in sandwiches.